cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image restoration and segmentation, which are primarily computer vision problems, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves probabilistic models and algorithms, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG). The numerical experiments involve computations and optimization, which are related to numerical analysis (cs.NA) and multimedia (cs.MM).
